<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c3">{هَاشِمٌ الرِّفَاعِي بِتَصَرُّفٍ يَسِير}</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">كُنْتُ إِذَا مَا ذَهَبْتُ لِزِيَارَتِهِ:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>أُحَدِّقُ فِيهِ وَفي المَكْتَبَة * كَمَا تَفْعَلُ الْقِطَّةُ الطَّيِّبَة<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
